**Overview**

This dashboard is designed to provide a comprehensive overview of the ServiceNow, focusing on services and their associated locations.

It presents key metrics related to configuration items, showcasing the operational and installation statuses of services, as well as highlighting the top business units and discovery sources.

The dashboard also includes visualizations that break down services by their intended use, support groups, and categories, which allows for effortless monitoring and management of service performance across various locations.
